7 excavations or roadway obstructions;
8 16. Any claim which is limited or barred by any other law;
9 17. Misrepresentation, if unintentional;
10 18. An act or omission of an independent contractor or
11 consultant or his or her employees, agents, subcontractors or
12 suppliers or of a person other than an employee of the state or
